uction of the relevant\nparameter space. We conclude by discussing the perspectives of microscopic\nmodelling in the field of active gels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Oct 2013 08:38:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Feb 2014 18:52:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
